Bart   Spriester  Senior Vice President of Video Products, Harmonic Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.48$677,936As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Bart Spriester has been Senior Vice President of Video Products at Harmonic Inc. since joining it on September 2, 2014. Mr. Spriester leads Harmonic’s Video Product Management and Solutions organization. Prior to joining Harmonic, he served as Chief Technology Officer, Executive Vice President and General Manager of North America at Encompass Digital Media, Inc. He joined Encompass from Cisco Systems, Inc/Scientific Atlanta where he served as Vice President and General ... Manager for Digital Media Networks. In his 19-year career with Cisco/Scientific Atlantic, he was involved in emerging technology development including that of advanced video streaming technologies, product strategy and various executive management positions such as Managing Director for EMEA Video Division. Prior to Cisco, Mr. Spriester worked for the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers (DoD) as a research engineer designing and testing electroacoustic warfare systems. He has over 20 years of experience in the media and video delivery infrastructure industry. He is an industry author of several publications and a noted engineer with several patents related to video delivery infrastructure. Mr. Spriester earned his B.S. in Electrical Engineering at the University of Illinois and his M.S. in Management from the Georgia Institute of Technology.Read Full Background




